1. The following information about the payment service provider—
(a) the name of the payment service provider;
(b) the address and contact details of the payment service provider's head office;
(c) if different from the information under sub-paragraph (b), the address and contact details 
of the branch or agent from which the payment service is being provided;
(d) details of the payment service provider's regulators, including any reference or registration 
number of the payment service provider.

